{"tid":1541374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民間記者會：五大訴求是港人共識　抗爭者沒收貨本錢","createTime":"2019-09-04T14:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T02:24:37.000Z","uid":20933,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7c999c0573695209e19071124d2f0490a45e0e8b","tid":1541374,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:27:37.000Z","msg":"民間記者會表示，香港人在超過80日抗爭中，明確提出五大訴求，而特首林鄭月娥在超過兩個月後，才宣布撤回修訂草案，回應社會6月初最強烈的訴求，形容是「太遲」、「太少」、「完全無用」，強調「五大訴求，缺一不可」是香港人的共識、原則及信念，抗爭者絕對不接受政府現時的回應，亦沒有收貨的本錢。<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會提到，有調查顯示，成立獨立調查委員會的呼聲比起撤回修例更高，又質疑監警會是「無牙老虎」，委任兩名新成員入監警會能否滿足市民對真相的渇求，又說新成員之一、前教育署署長余黎青萍早已表明，反修例事件不適宜設立獨立調查委員會，因此難以相信監警會能不偏不倚展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會指出，反修例示威，反映香港恆之有效的制度是殘破不堪，例如出現警方濫權及白色恐怖等，並非一句簡單「撤回」，就可以彌補。"},{"pid":"7e208485016d0daef030a90b1cf6d9d738f44764","tid":1541374,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:27:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478825-20190904.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478825-20190904.htm&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=a21d3704\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478825-20190904.htm&h=5f3e7b7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478825-20190904.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3a1c58d84f99bebebbd3392856af8e83319010df","tid":1541374,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:28:28.000Z","msg":"林鄭又撚鳩我地喇！<br />\n立法會議事規則列明撤回法案只需「宣佈」，不需「動議」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dONuKS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dONuKS</a>"},{"pid":"cdaa0775d8a32a6d06356c85805d7afe6706de90","tid":1541374,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:29:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a995949daa7e246eddd4ad193ef3234dddc1c3cf","tid":1541374,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c6eef19d3b3c6772a526d15201346e2d3caae6","tid":1541374,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e79bc1786a0c0120d487c79607bb8aac24ac3b","tid":1541374,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0156ff420f534694ad43d1079cc6cbd5848a17b","tid":1541374,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:54:15.000Z","msg":"［核彈］政府撤例，建制無能，白票洩憤，射比對家都唔益建制<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1541383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1541383</a><br /